{"title":"Leetcode第25题：K 个一组翻转链表","slug":"2019092701","date":"2019-09-27T10:39:23.000Z","updated":"2019-09-27T11:12:41.000Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/2019092701.json","excerpt":"题目给你一个链表，每 k 个节点一组进行翻转，请你返回翻转后的链表。","covers":["https://ae01.alicdn.com/kf/H91317be2c31148b4866c9e1200c1beb0b.png","https://ae01.alicdn.com/kf/Hc5bde4194d1a4596bbbe570668baa64aB.png"],"content":"<h2 id=\"题目\"><a href=\"#题目\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"题目\"></a>题目</h2><p>给你一个链表，每 k 个节点一组进行翻转，请你返回翻转后的链表。</p>\n<a id=\"more\"></a>\n<p>k 是一个正整数，它的值小于或等于链表的长度。<br>如果节点总数不是 k 的整数倍，那么请将最后剩余的节点保持原有顺序。<br><strong>示例 :</strong></p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>给定这个链表：1-&gt;2-&gt;3-&gt;4-&gt;5<br>当 k = 2 时，应当返回: 2-&gt;1-&gt;4-&gt;3-&gt;5<br>当 k = 3 时，应当返回: 3-&gt;2-&gt;1-&gt;4-&gt;5</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p><strong>说明 :</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>你的算法只能使用常数的额外空间。</li>\n<li>你不能只是单纯的改变节点内部的值，而是需要实际的进行节点交换。</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"代码\"><a href=\"#代码\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"代码\"></a>代码</h2><figure class=\"highlight java\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br><span class=\"line\">15</span><br><span class=\"line\">16</span><br><span class=\"line\">17</span><br><span class=\"line\">18</span><br><span class=\"line\">19</span><br><span class=\"line\">20</span><br><span class=\"line\">21</span><br><span class=\"line\">22</span><br><span class=\"line\">23</span><br><span class=\"line\">24</span><br><span class=\"line\">25</span><br><span class=\"line\">26</span><br><span class=\"line\">27</span><br><span class=\"line\">28</span><br><span class=\"line\">29</span><br><span class=\"line\">30</span><br><span class=\"line\">31</span><br><span class=\"line\">32</span><br><span class=\"line\">33</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">/**</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"> * Definition for singly-linked list.</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"> * public class ListNode &#123;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"> *     int val;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"> *     ListNode next;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"> *     ListNode(int x) &#123; val = x; &#125;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"> * &#125;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"> */</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"class\"><span class=\"keyword\">class</span> <span class=\"title\">Solution</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"function\"><span class=\"keyword\">public</span> ListNode <span class=\"title\">reverseKGroup</span><span class=\"params\">(ListNode head, <span class=\"keyword\">int</span> k)</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        ListNode result=<span class=\"keyword\">new</span> ListNode(<span class=\"number\">0</span>);</span><br><span class=\"line\">            ListNode tmp=<span class=\"keyword\">new</span> ListNode(<span class=\"number\">0</span>);</span><br><span class=\"line\">            result.next=tmp;</span><br><span class=\"line\">            List&lt;ListNode&gt; list=<span class=\"keyword\">new</span> ArrayList&lt;&gt;();</span><br><span class=\"line\">            <span class=\"keyword\">while</span>(head!=<span class=\"keyword\">null</span>) &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">                list.add(head);</span><br><span class=\"line\">                head=head.next;</span><br><span class=\"line\">                <span class=\"keyword\">if</span>(list.size()==k) &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">                    <span class=\"keyword\">for</span>(<span class=\"keyword\">int</span> i=list.size()-<span class=\"number\">1</span>;i&gt;=<span class=\"number\">0</span>;i--) &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">                        tmp.next=list.get(i);</span><br><span class=\"line\">                        list.remove(i);</span><br><span class=\"line\">                        tmp=tmp.next;</span><br><span class=\"line\">                    &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">                &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">            &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">            <span class=\"keyword\">for</span>(<span class=\"keyword\">int</span> i=<span class=\"number\">0</span>;i&lt;list.size();i++) &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">                tmp.next=list.get(i);</span><br><span class=\"line\">                tmp=tmp.next;</span><br><span class=\"line\">            &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">            tmp.next=<span class=\"keyword\">null</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">            <span class=\"keyword\">return</span> result.next.next;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h3 id=\"运行结果\"><a href=\"#运行结果\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"运行结果\"></a>运行结果</h3><p><img src=\"https://ae01.alicdn.com/kf/H91317be2c31148b4866c9e1200c1beb0b.png\"></p>\n<h2 id=\"总结\"><a href=\"#总结\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"总结\"></a>总结</h2><p>这道题虽然和<a href=\"https://www.thzone.cn/20190925/2019092501/\">第24题</a>很相似，但是我的24题的解法是行不通的，而目前这个方法的思想是参考了Leetcode社区里一位大佬的思想的：<br><img src=\"https://ae01.alicdn.com/kf/Hc5bde4194d1a4596bbbe570668baa64aB.png\"><br>新建一个存储ListNode的List，根据head节点的next是否为空进行while循环，将每个节点依次添加到list里，当list的size等于k时，就开始将list中每次的最后一位取出接到结果的next节点里，while循环结束后还是需要处理一下list中的剩余ListNode（不足以逆序排列的），将他们正序添加到结果即可。其实这种方法就是使用了栈的特性，先进后出实现逆序，不过在使用这种思想时还是新建了一个ArrayList，感觉违反了题意，但是依然AC了，所以还是可行的。<br><img src=\"https://ae01.alicdn.com/kf/Hf9c41f8800864387a1ca377dfd743525E.png\"></p>\n","more":"<p>k 是一个正整数，它的值小于或等于链表的长度。<br>如果节点总数不是 k 的整数倍，那么请将最后剩余的节点保持原有顺序。<br><strong>示例 :</strong></p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>给定这个链表：1-&gt;2-&gt;3-&gt;4-&gt;5<br>当 k = 2 时，应当返回: 2-&gt;1-&gt;4-&gt;3-&gt;5<br>当 k = 3 时，应当返回: 3-&gt;2-&gt;1-&gt;4-&gt;5</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p><strong>说明 :</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>你的算法只能使用常数的额外空间。</li>\n<li>你不能只是单纯的改变节点内部的值，而是需要实际的进行节点交换。</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"代码\"><a href=\"#代码\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"代码\"></a>代码</h2><figure class=\"highlight java\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br><span class=\"line\">15</span><br><span class=\"line\">16</span><br><span class=\"line\">17</span><br><span class=\"line\">18</span><br><span class=\"line\">19</span><br><span class=\"line\">20</span><br><span class=\"line\">21</span><br><span class=\"line\">22</span><br><span class=\"line\">23</span><br><span class=\"line\">24</span><br><span class=\"line\">25</span><br><span class=\"line\">26</span><br><span class=\"line\">27</span><br><span class=\"line\">28</span><br><span class=\"line\">29</span><br><span class=\"line\">30</span><br><span class=\"line\">31</span><br><span class=\"line\">32</span><br><span class=\"line\">33</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">/**</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"> * Definition for singly-linked list.</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"> * public class ListNode &#123;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"> *     int val;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"> *     ListNode next;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"> *     ListNode(int x) &#123; val = x; &#125;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"> * &#125;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"> */</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"class\"><span class=\"keyword\">class</span> <span class=\"title\">Solution</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"function\"><span class=\"keyword\">public</span> ListNode <span class=\"title\">reverseKGroup</span><span class=\"params\">(ListNode head, <span class=\"keyword\">int</span> k)</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        ListNode result=<span class=\"keyword\">new</span> ListNode(<span class=\"number\">0</span>);</span><br><span class=\"line\">            ListNode tmp=<span class=\"keyword\">new</span> ListNode(<span class=\"number\">0</span>);</span><br><span class=\"line\">            result.next=tmp;</span><br><span class=\"line\">            List&lt;ListNode&gt; list=<span class=\"keyword\">new</span> ArrayList&lt;&gt;();</span><br><span class=\"line\">            <span class=\"keyword\">while</span>(head!=<span class=\"keyword\">null</span>) &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">                list.add(head);</span><br><span class=\"line\">                head=head.next;</span><br><span class=\"line\">                <span class=\"keyword\">if</span>(list.size()==k) &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">                    <span class=\"keyword\">for</span>(<span class=\"keyword\">int</span> i=list.size()-<span class=\"number\">1</span>;i&gt;=<span class=\"number\">0</span>;i--) &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">                        tmp.next=list.get(i);</span><br><span class=\"line\">                        list.remove(i);</span><br><span class=\"line\">                        tmp=tmp.next;</span><br><span class=\"line\">                    &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">                &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">            &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">            <span class=\"keyword\">for</span>(<span class=\"keyword\">int</span> i=<span class=\"number\">0</span>;i&lt;list.size();i++) &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">                tmp.next=list.get(i);</span><br><span class=\"line\">                tmp=tmp.next;</span><br><span class=\"line\">            &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">            tmp.next=<span class=\"keyword\">null</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">            <span class=\"keyword\">return</span> result.next.next;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h3 id=\"运行结果\"><a href=\"#运行结果\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"运行结果\"></a>运行结果</h3><p><img src=\"https://ae01.alicdn.com/kf/H91317be2c31148b4866c9e1200c1beb0b.png\"></p>\n<h2 id=\"总结\"><a href=\"#总结\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"总结\"></a>总结</h2><p>这道题虽然和<a href=\"https://www.thzone.cn/20190925/2019092501/\">第24题</a>很相似，但是我的24题的解法是行不通的，而目前这个方法的思想是参考了Leetcode社区里一位大佬的思想的：<br><img src=\"https://ae01.alicdn.com/kf/Hc5bde4194d1a4596bbbe570668baa64aB.png\"><br>新建一个存储ListNode的List，根据head节点的next是否为空进行while循环，将每个节点依次添加到list里，当list的size等于k时，就开始将list中每次的最后一位取出接到结果的next节点里，while循环结束后还是需要处理一下list中的剩余ListNode（不足以逆序排列的），将他们正序添加到结果即可。其实这种方法就是使用了栈的特性，先进后出实现逆序，不过在使用这种思想时还是新建了一个ArrayList，感觉违反了题意，但是依然AC了，所以还是可行的。<br><img src=\"https://ae01.alicdn.com/kf/Hf9c41f8800864387a1ca377dfd743525E.png\"></p>","categories":[{"name":"开发","path":"api/categories/开发.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"JAVA","path":"api/tags/JAVA.json"},{"name":"算法","path":"api/tags/算法.json"}]}